<Layout 
	title="Gadget Fix - Fast Mobile Electronics Repair Dallas-Fort Worth"
	description="Professional mobile electronics repair in Dallas-Fort Worth. Smartphones, tablets, gadgets - expert technicians, warranty included, on-site service available. Call (402) 416-6942"
	keywords="mobile phone repair Dallas, smartphone repair Fort Worth, tablet repair, screen repair, battery replacement, water damage repair, electronics repair DFW"
